            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "=You are a trading result analysis engine.\n\nInput is a JSON array of rows with:\n- ma_lenh (base trade id, string)\n- tp_loss (TP1, TP2, TP3, ... or Loss)\n- rr (numeric R value, positive or negative)\n\nRules:\n1. Analyze rows grouped by ma_lenh independently.\n2. If ANY row of a ma_lenh is a Loss OR rr < 0:\n   - Select the rr from the Loss row.\n   - Set tp_hit = \"Loss\".\n   - reason = \"loss\".\n3. If there is NO Loss:\n   - Select the row with the HIGHEST rr among TP rows.\n   - Set tp_hit to the corresponding TP label (e.g. TP1, TP2, TP3).\n   - reason = \"max_tp\".\n4. Do NOT average rr.\n5. Do NOT sum rr.\n6. Output EXACTLY one record per ma_lenh.\n7. Output JSON ONLY. No explanation text.\n\nOutput format:\n[\n  {\n    \"ID_Post\": \"<string>\",\n    \"final_rr\": <number>,\n    \"tp_hit\": \"<TPx | Loss>\",\n    \"reason\": \"loss\" | \"max_tp\"\n  }\n]\n"
            }
          ]
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
